    <h1 {...{
      "id": "installation"
    }}>{`Installation`}</h1>
    <p>{`Before setting up Kerberos Enterprise, some configuration needs to happen. First thing that we need to do is setting up the RBAC permissions (Role Based Access Control). We need to enable this to be able to query specific endpoints from the Kubernetes API. By default these endpoints are locked, so we need to unlock them.`}</p>
    <br />
    <div class='embed-container'><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/404767375" width="640" height="400" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
