          "className": "vscode-highlight-line"
        }}>{`kubectl create -n kerberos -f ./enterprise/yaml/factory/clusterrole.yaml`}</span></code></pre>
    <p>{`This will make several actions inside your cluster available. We need this to be able to create deployments from the factory web app.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "helm"
