    <h2 {...{
      "id": "traefik"
    }}>{`Traefik`}</h2>
    <p><a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://containo.us/traefik/"
      }}><strong parentName="a">{`Traefik`}</strong></a>{` is a reverse proxy and load balancer which allows you to expose your deployments more easily. Kerberos uses Traefik to expose it's APIs more easily.`}</p>
    <p>{`By executing following helm command, we will install traefik and link it to a specific DNS name. Open the traefik values file, `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`./enterprise/yaml/traefik/values.yaml`}</inlineCode>{`, and update the DNS name to your own domain.`}</p>
