    <p>{`After installation you should have an IP attached to traefik service, look for it by executing the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`get service`}</inlineCode>{` command. You will see the ip address in the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`EXTERNAL-IP`}</inlineCode>{` attribute.`}</p>
